{
  "id": "69c114d2689b393065911c75",
  "title": "Floorp",
  "created": 1774261464,
  "updated": 1774262449,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c114d2689b393065911c75",
      "text": "Floorp",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774261464,
      "updated": 1774261464
    },
    {
      "id": "69c114d70000000000e01890",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774261464,
      "updated": 1774261464
    },
    {
      "id": "69c114d90000000000e01893",
      "text": "日本の[Ablaze]が開発を主導する実質的な[Firefox]ベースの実質的な[Vivaldi]代替",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774261465,
      "updated": 1774261965
    },
    {
      "id": "69c1168a0000000000e0189c",
      "text": "[opensource]だから厳密には国産ではないとはいえ、海外でも著名な[国産ソフト]の一角を占めている",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774261898,
      "updated": 1774262449
    },
    {
      "id": "69c1153a0000000000e01898",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774261562,
      "updated": 1774261562
    },
    {
      "id": "69c1153c0000000000e0189a",
      "text": "無印[Firefox]にない[PWA]も独自に対応していたりと、何かと高機能",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774261564,
      "updated": 1774261605
    },
    {
      "id": "69c116eb0000000000e018a1",
      "text": "もちろん[Vivaldi]代替だから多機能サブバーもある",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774261995,
      "updated": 1774262045
    },
    {
      "id": "69c116f80000000000e018a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774262008,
      "updated": 1774262008
    },
    {
      "id": "69c116d70000000000e018a0",
      "text": "今までのFirefoxフォークは大きく分けて",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774261975,
      "updated": 1774262180
    },
    {
      "id": "69c1172b0000000000e018a3",
      "text": " 旧規格の拡張機能の動作",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774262059,
      "updated": 1774262080
    },
    {
      "id": "69c1153b0000000000e01899",
      "text": " プライバシー機能拡充",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774261564,
      "updated": 1774262094
    },
    {
      "id": "69c1174d0000000000e018a5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774262094,
      "updated": 1774262094
    },
    {
      "id": "69c1174e0000000000e018a6",
      "text": "の二つの方向性があって、そこに機能性を重視するフォークはなかったためその手のソフトが好きなFirefoxユーザーに歓迎されている",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774262094,
      "updated": 1774262365
    },
    {
      "id": "69c1172d0000000000e018a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774262062,
      "updated": 1774262062
    },
    {
      "id": "69c1186c0000000000e018a9",
      "text": "最近巷で話題の[Zen Browser]も[Floorp]のコードを流用しているとのウワサ",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774262381,
      "updated": 1774262414
    },
    {
      "id": "69c1186c0000000000e018aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774262381,
      "updated": 1774262381
    },
    {
      "id": "69c114d70000000000e01891",
      "text": "[Floorp ブラウザー https://ja.floorp.app/]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774261499,
      "updated": 1774261499
    },
    {
      "id": "69c115320000000000e01895",
      "text": " 公式サイト",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774261554,
      "updated": 1774261557
    },
    {
      "id": "69c118910000000000e018ab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1774262417,
      "updated": 1774262417
    }
  ]
}